io.hekate.cluster.event

Interface ClusterEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HekateSupport
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClusterChangeEvent, ClusterEventBase, ClusterJoinEvent, ClusterLeaveEvent

    public interface ClusterEvent
extends HekateSupport
    Cluster event. This is the base interface for all events that can be fired by the ClusterService.
    See Also:
    ClusterEventListener, ClusterService
